.DT 
set_random_stats 
Discworld monster help 
set_random_stats 

Name
.SI 5
set_random_stats - Sets up random stat values.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_random_stats(int no, int type);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This sets up a bunch of random stats, it rolls the type dice no times
and sets up the stats that way.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
stats
.EP
